  "label": "Umbravolt Grotto",
  "description": "Umbravolt Grotto is a basalt cave hollowed into Vespera Tertius’ ash-choked crust, its walls vitrified into black glass by repeated electrostatic strikes. Bruise-colored auroral light filters through narrow roof fissures, casting oil-slick iridescence across jagged flowstone and slag-like drips. The floor forms a shallow basin of fine ash and magnetized grit that clings to boots and tools, while intermittent violet lightning outside drives a low, resonant tremor through the rock. Vox signals degrade sharply within the chamber, reduced to sputtering fragments amid persistent static hiss.",
